<p>[2]https://www.tepco.co.jp/en/decommission/progress/watertreatment/index-e.html </p>
<p>[3] GB6249-2011 核动力厂辐射防护规定 </p>
<p>[4] GB5749-2006 生活饮用水卫生标准 </p>
